msg: JDO-597 Add ReadOnly property to PMF: jdoconfig_2_2.dtd

author: asmuts
msg: Adding the ability to inject both event loggers and custom serializers into auxiliaries.  The event loggers will make JCS far easier to monitor.  The custom serializers will allow you to do things such as have JCS compress your items prior to storage.  This is still a work in progress.  I have more to do.
